# Vivendo Entre Dolores

Read [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) for full context. Key constraints:

- Static GitHub Pages site — no build step, vanilla HTML/CSS/JS
- **Never commit** `.env` or `config.local.json` (secrets)
- Supabase project ref: `gduyitvnnyuewwbebeyq` — dashboard: https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/gduyitvnnyuewwbebeyq
- DB migrations: use pooler `aws-1-sa-east-1.pooler.supabase.com` or `./scripts/run-supabase-migration.sh` — not direct `db.*` host (IPv6-only)
- Guestbook EN / Deixar um Recado PT — same `recados` table; `post_slug` null = general, set = post message
- Social share card image: `contato.html` only (post picker), not on post pages
- i18n: always update both `locales/pt-BR.json` and `locales/en-US.json`
- Posts: `{slug}/index.html` from `templates/post-template.html`; include `data-mural-section` + `data-post-slug`
- Sync Supabase keys to site: `./scripts/sync-mural-config.sh`

Detailed Supabase connection: [docs/SUPABASE.md](docs/SUPABASE.md)
